/target
**/*.rs.bk
# Cargo.lock IS tracked: this workspace builds deployed wasm binaries (an app),
# so pinning deps keeps CI reproducible — an unpinned wasm-bindgen drifted to a
# newer glue form than local and broke the Firefox patch in CI.
bin/
pkg/
crates/*/pkg/
!crates/*/pkg/*.d.ts
wasm-pack.log
app/node_modules/
app/dist/
app/.tests-dist/
docs/*
.DS_Store
.claude
engineering-codex
